ONITSHA – Reactions have continued trailing the selfless and leadership qualities of the former Governor of Anambra State, Mr Peter Obi. Speaking on this development, the CEO Rojenny Tourist/Games Village Oba, Chief Rommy Ezeonwuka showered encomiums to former Governor of Anambra State, His Excellency, Mr. Peter Obi, on his leadership style and described him as a Leader who recognizes his friends both in and outside politics. Ezeonwuka dropped that hint yesterday at the residence of the CEO INNOSON VEHICLE MANUFACTURING, High Chief Innoson Chukwuma (Ifeadiaso)in Nnewi Anambra State. Security Beefed At APC Secretariat After National Convention… Ebonyi Assembly Declares Deputy Speaker’s Seat Vacant,… Recalling further on former Governor Obi days as the Governor of the State, he said that the former Governor released funds to upgrade the sports and tourism facilities at Rojenny village Oba. According to him ,Obi introduce Gov. Willie Obiano to the facility, and admonished him to always support the upgrade of the facility by giving out grants. Chief Rommy Ezeonwuka invested a fortune in Rojenny, therefore should always be encouraged because such investment would attract bigger returns if it were to be in Abuja or Lagos. While speaking to our reporter, Chief Ezeonwuka described the former Governor as good spirited man whose benevolence cuts across religious or political affiliations. In his words, His Excellency, Mr. Peter Obi is an astute and selfless leader whose Government supported privates investors and created an enabling environment for investments to thrive. POLL He noted that his support to Rojenny Games Village were immense and pledged that he will continue remaining grateful to him for the work he did during his tenure. Ezeonwuka further described Peter Obi as a leader who accommodates everyone.